title: Denim Nightmare with Joe Derosa | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 71
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
Chrissy D is out sick this week babes!!!! Sal is joined by the TASTE BUDDY HIMSELF Joe Derosa!! But Chris does take over the show at one point hahhahahah CHAOS BABES CHAOS!!! Sal is working on a new ransom note bit. Do we think it's a good idea?!?
